welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Fish Hawk! This charming city is known for its breathtaking natural beauty and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all it has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Municipal Airport handles all air freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free wifi network for internet access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport serves both civilian and military passengers.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport is dedicated to serving military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport houses the majority of the airport's facilities, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and various shops and restaurants.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily international and charter flights.

terminals.name: Airside E
terminals.description: Airside E is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Airside F
terminals.description: Airside F is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily domestic flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport. Connect to the 'TPA-Free-WiFi' network and accept the terms and conditions to access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bartow Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Bartow Airport handles all cargo and freight shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Whitted Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Whitted Airport is reserved for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at St. Petersburg-Clearwater International Airport is a modern and spacious facility with a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Airside Terminal
terminals.description: The airside terminal at St. Petersburg-Clearwater International Airport offers a convenient and efficient way for travelers to access their flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
